{"tid":1078392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【洩露天機】英超宣佈亞洲行 意外透露曼城會贏冠軍","createTime":"2019-03-26T09:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:37:14.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9b7c7ff9a30544e3a7bdeb7b8aa52b76f3db92","tid":1078392,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"今屆英超比賽已經進入白熱化階段，冠軍極大機會落入曼城或利物浦手中，正當比賽去到最後直路，日前英超官方公佈今夏亞洲之旅時，竟然疑似「洩露天機」，預告曼城將會贏得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n英超官方於今日 ( 26 日 ) 宣佈，將會在今年夏天在中國舉行「英超亞洲盃」，參賽球隊包括曼城、紐卡素、韋斯咸和狼隊，其中帖文提到這次是時隔十年後，英超亞洲盃再度於中國內地舉行，並特別寫到「同時也首次有英超衛冕冠軍參加到該項賽事當中」。<br />\n<br />\n英超 FB 專頁，按圖可放大。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民指出帖文中的「衛冕冠軍」無疑是指曼城，與此同時，官方的英文版宣傳中，亦有「衛冕冠軍」的字眼，認為官方洩露天機，暗示曼城將會贏得今屆英超。"},{"pid":"131e985466240ed80957833f75a782fb222ab3aa","tid":1078392,"uid":230239,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:28:00.000Z","msg":"衛冕冠軍係解Defending Champion喎，唔等於衛冕成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492c047affbe482ee138d36ef298984eda76b039","tid":1078392,"uid":102356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fc665e98d8fdcefe8055440079d71f90491eca","tid":1078392,"uid":743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:32:42.000Z","msg":"而家啲記者真係唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eafcc13343d0bb5a5aeada54dba9c780c5834a1","tid":1078392,"uid":69568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:32:45.000Z","msg":"唔識英文都做到記者 reigning champion係解應屆冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122591a0cdfd022c4648fd01dd9a6e93d4267cbf","tid":1078392,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T20:55: